topic: Sport Workflow Series ("F1 pilots explorative search")

goals.1: Identify the BGP for obtaining the team of a given  F1 driver  and also the F1 competitions in which they participated
goals.2: Identify the BGP that connects a F1 team to a parent company
goals.3: How many F1 drivers and F1 teams exist in each country?
